%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
flowchart LR
    subgraph EPMS["EPMS - MZ Zone"]
        UI[EPMS UI / BFF]
        JO[Journey Orchestrator]
        BMS[Business Microservices]
        IMS[Integration Adapter for JIRA<br/>EKS Deployment]
        MB[Message Broker]
        SYNC[WBS Sync Consumer]
        WBSDB[(EPMS WBS DB)]
        READ[Reporting / Gantt Read Model]
        MAP[(Type Mapping / Source Link Table)]
        DLQ[Dead Letter Queue]
        REC[Reconciliation Scheduler]
    end

    subgraph JIRA_ZONE["JIRA"]
        JIRA[JIRA Project / Space]
        WH[JIRA Webhooks]
        API[JIRA REST APIs]
        ADM[JIRA Administrator]
    end

    UI -->|Create JIRA space| JO
    JO -->|Invoke integration| IMS
    IMS -->|Create project/space API| API
    API --> ADM
    API -->|Space created response| IMS
    IMS -->|Link JIRA project key| BMS

    JIRA -->|Issue create/update/delete| WH
    WH -->|Webhook callback| IMS
    IMS -->|Validate / normalize / dedupe| MB
    MB --> SYNC
    SYNC --> MAP
    SYNC -->|Upsert WBS hierarchy| WBSDB
    SYNC -->|Refresh reporting view| READ

    REC -->|Updated since cursor| IMS
    IMS -->|Incremental pull / JQL search| API
    API -->|Changed issues batch| IMS
    IMS -->|Bulk sync events| MB

    MB --> DLQ